Contents of Mushroom disk 43                                 2 Disks
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                                 ~~~~~~~

ý
    This is the shareware version of this magazine, Extreme AMOS 1. Recently
reviewed in Amiga Computing, it was stated as being reccomended to look at.

    On the first disk, is all the articles me + Carl have written,
including my Equalizer tutorial, and Tracker tutorial. These both come with
example programs, so you can load them straight into AMOS.

    The whole lot is controlled by an impressive engine Carl wrote, similar
to this Mushroom PD engine.

    On the second disk comes 2 compiled programs, both of which were
written in AMOS. Here they are in a bit of detail :





