                               Piles'O'Tiles
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ý
    This is an amazing little puzzle game created by that AMOS god, Paul
Burkey. Remeber the Shanghai games? Well this is a jolly good
representation of these. There has been a total facelift when it comes to
the tiles, including pictures of Mushrooms, Cars, Faces, Disks, Flags, and
loads of others. I am told that the full-version has the original tileset
available as well.

    I highly reccomend this game, as with all of Paul Burkeys games, it has
that amazingly playable feeling.

