                         TERDS Stereogram creator
                         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ý
    This is the second program on the disk. It was written by Carl, and it
allows you to create and save those horrible RDS pictures, you know, the
ones with all those millions of coloured dots.

ÿ
ý
    Carl and a couple of others tell me that they work, but I cannot see
nothing in them. If you like these stereogram pictures, then this program
is for you. Everything is controlled via on-screen menus for ease of use.
The registered version also has animation under the mouse etc. included, as
well as all the options turned on.


    Only the shareware version of Extreme AMOS is freely distributable
across all possible forms of media transfer, providing no more than 1
pound is charged.

